Okay, I understand. I need to create a JSON array that represents actions to operate accounting software. The actions should include clicking on account input fields, entering amounts, adding memos, and posting/saving the transaction.

<OUTPUT_JSON>[{"action": "click", "selector": "input[name*=account i]", "text": ""}, {"action": "fill", "selector": "input[name*=amount i]", "text": "100"}, {"action": "fill", "selector": "textarea[name*=memo i]", "text": "Test transaction"}, {"action": "click", "selector": "button:has-text(\"post\" i)"}]</OUTPUT_JSON>
